verbose_text: Secondary outcomes included the following : Bioavailability of metformin, estimated from the amount of metformin excreted in the urine over 24 h; AUC of metformin absorption from 0-24 h (AUC 0-24 h); Time to peak drug concentration (T max) and peak plasma drug concentration (C max); and AUC of plasma glucose levels over the first 8 h of sampling (AUC 0-8h).
